text: Dennis Störl (born 3 October 1979) is a retired German ski jumper. In the World Cup he finished once among the top 15, with an eleventh place from Willingen in February 2001. He finished third overall in the Continental Cup in the 1990/00 season. ==External links== * Category:1979 births Category:Living people Category:German male ski jumpers
